Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.76,0:00:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样珠里 好久不见哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 好久不见哥哥\N好久不见啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.16,0:00:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧 我自己拉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.27,0:01:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚放学吗 别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.01,0:01:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.74,0:01:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.21,0:01:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未华子也刚放学吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.35,0:01:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.45,0:01:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.99,0:01:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.37,0:01:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热 别这样 有什么关系\N反正姐姐也不搂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.41,0:01:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没有回省与妹妹瞒着父母\N近亲相奸并中出 迹美珠里 安部未华子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.65,0:01:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里完全没变啊 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.75,0:01:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 吃这个 好 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.69,0:02:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 吃这个\N爸爸做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.60,0:02:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃 张嘴\N真是的 还没说开动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.00,0:02:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了 先吃了\N爸爸你也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.74,0:02:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开动吧 好 我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.95,0:02:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 张嘴 别这样\N别这么油腻 哥哥会困扰的 才没困扰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.89,0:02:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 好吃吧 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.09,0:02:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗 好吃那再吃一个吗\N来 哥哥 张嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.64,0:02:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗 好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.54,0:02:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再吃一个吗 好 张嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.55,0:03:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你也说点什么啊\N话说你已经出去三年了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.49,0:03:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.19,0:03:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有女朋友了吗 没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.60,0:03:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该考虑这些了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.24,0:03:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个工作太忙了\N结婚什么的还早呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.54,0:03:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家就好了 我和你结婚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.21,0:03:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说什么蠢话 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.55,0:03:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你学学你姐姐 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.79,0:03:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃啊 这个\N还能吃吗 能啊 这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.30,0:04:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠里
